Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam！！
